title: Kanye West Has Plans To Compete With Kylie Jenner's Cosmetics Business! Is A Family Feud Going To Break Out?! CocoPerez.com
text:
A little competition is healthy, but this might hit Kylie Jenner a bit too close at home!
As we've previously reported, the 19-year-old Kylie Cosmetics founder is constantly selling out of her lip kits, shadows, and soon, her new highlighters !
But after trailing in the footsteps of her big sisters' Kardashian Beauty line, how does she feel about Kanye West coming for the beauty business??
Related: Twitter Reacts To Kanye's Yeezy Show!
According to TMZ , the rapper is following up on his plans to create a cosmetics line in honor of his late momma, Donda West , who passed in 2007.
Kanye filed legal papers to make the dream a reality, filling out an application for the DONDA brand to sell makeup, perfumes, and more beauty-related products. It has yet to be approved, but this is only the start for the poppa of two.
At his Yeezy fashion show last year, 'Ye unveiled his video game inspired by his momma, Only One: The Game , and teased a whole slew of business ideas in her honor!
Ch-ch-check it all out (below) and let us know what U think!
Do U think Kylizzle will try to stop her brother-in-law from entering the beauty world??
